    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked with a slight bite, drain the <strong>rice noodles</strong> and set aside</p>",
