    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice noodles</strong> in a bowl and top with the <strong>pork bun cha</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining nuoc cham </strong>to the side and drizzle over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli rounds</strong>, <strong>chopped mint </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Serve<strong> </strong>the <strong>quick-pickled nuoc cham mooli slaw </strong>to the side and enjoy!</p>",
